title: The Rick and Morty show is amazing
content: You don't have to try to impress me Morty. Right, Crocubot. So, you're half cold unfeeling reptile, half also cold equally unfeeling machine? Do you know how many characters there are in the Simpsons Morty? There's like a-a billion characters, M-Morty. There was an episode where Former President BUSH was their neighbor! Burgertime!

title: Rick for President
content: What are you looking at, mother fucker! Is he keeping his shoulders square? Oooooooh he's tryin'! Listen, Morty, I hate to break it to you but what people call love is just a chemical reaction that compels animals to breed. I'm your worst nightmare, bitch!

title: Nothing great happens in Mortyville
content: I love burgers! I don't know man, Italy, Greece, Argentina... Okay, take it easy Rick. T-that's dark. It's called carpe diem Morty. Look it up.
